-- TAKE A LOOK-Australia says hopes rise in search for missing Malaysian jet
-- 
-- Sat Mar 22, 2014 11:03PM EDT
-- None



March 23 (Reuters) - Australia's prime minister says there is "increasing hope" of a breakthrough in the hunt for missing Malaysian airliner MH370, carrying 239 people, after Chinese satellite images showed what could be debris within a search area deep in the southern Indian Ocean.

